Class Cliente

java.lang.Object
edu.uptc.Entidades.Usuario
edu.uptc.Entidades.Cliente
public class Cliente extends Usuario
Represents a client in the system. Extends Usuario and adds client-specific functionality including plan management and PQRS tracking. Clients can subscribe to multiple plans and submit PQRS (Petitions, Complaints, Claims, Suggestions).

      public Cliente(String cedula, String nombre, String apellido, LocalDate fechaNacimiento, String pais, String departamento, String ciudad, String numeroCelular, String contrasena)
      Constructs a new Cliente with the specified details. Initializes empty lists for plans and PQRS.
      Parameters:
      cedula - Client's identification number
      nombre - Client's first name
      apellido - Client's last name
      fechaNacimiento - Client's date of birth
      pais - Client's country
      departamento - Client's department/state
      ciudad - Client's city
      numeroCelular - Client's mobile phone number
      contrasena - Client's password
